# HTTP Client requests cho MinIO/file storage mini-lab
#
# File này chỉ chứa placeholder. Không paste access token thật vào Git.
#
# Điều kiện sau khi tự implement:
# - PostgreSQL/Keycloak/MinIO đang chạy.
# - tenant-demo đang chạy.
# - APP_FILE_STORAGE_ENABLED=true.
# - Bucket MinIO `tenant-demo-files` đã tồn tại.

@tenantDemoUrl = http://localhost:8080
@invalidToken = invalid.jwt.token

### MinIO health check trực tiếp
GET http://localhost:19000/minio/health/ready

### Local JWT fallback: lấy token tenant 1 - chỉ dùng local lab
GET {{tenantDemoUrl}}/api/dev/tokens/tenant-1?roles=ACCOUNTANT

### Local JWT fallback: lấy token tenant 2 - chỉ dùng local lab
GET {{tenantDemoUrl}}/api/dev/tokens/tenant-2?roles=ACCOUNTANT

# TODO: lấy token từ lab-code/keycloak-lab/http/keycloak-token-flow.http
# hoặc từ dev token endpoint local ở trên, rồi paste tạm vào IntelliJ
# private env/biến local không commit.
#@tenant1Token = <paste-keycloak-token-tenant-1-here>
#@tenant2Token = <paste-keycloak-token-tenant-2-here>
#@noRoleToken = <paste-keycloak-token-without-required-role-here>

# TODO: sau khi upload tenant 1, copy fileId từ response.
@tenant1FileId = <copy-file-id-from-upload-response>

### Upload file as tenant 1 -> expected 201
# IntelliJ HTTP Client sẽ đọc file local theo path bạn chọn.
# Đổi đường dẫn file test cho phù hợp máy local, không commit file thật nếu nhạy cảm.
POST {{tenantDemoUrl}}/api/files
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant1Token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello MinIO tenant-aware file storage lab.
--boundary--

### Download own file as tenant 1 -> expected 200
GET {{tenantDemoUrl}}/api/files/{{tenant1FileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant1Token}}

### Tenant 2 cannot download tenant 1 file -> expected 404/no leakage
GET {{tenantDemoUrl}}/api/files/{{tenant1FileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant2Token}}

### Missing token -> expected 401
GET {{tenantDemoUrl}}/api/files/{{tenant1FileId}}

### Invalid token -> expected 401
GET {{tenantDemoUrl}}/api/files/{{tenant1FileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{invalidToken}}

### Optional wrong role -> expected 403 trong APP_AUTH_MODE=keycloak
# Local JWT fallback chỉ test authenticated + tenant isolation, không phải RBAC chính.
GET {{tenantDemoUrl}}/api/files/{{tenant1FileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{noRoleToken}}

### Delete own file as tenant 1 -> expected 204
DELETE {{tenantDemoUrl}}/api/files/{{tenant1FileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant1Token}}

### Download after delete -> expected 404
GET {{tenantDemoUrl}}/api/files/{{tenant1FileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant1Token}}
